**Fortune Teller** | Townsfolk Investigative
__Basics__
Each night, the Fortune Teller may check one player’s role.
__Details__
Each night, the Fortune Teller can inspect a player. The Fortune Teller will be told what their role is.
Inspecting a player is an immediate ability. The Fortune Teller gains more information, but is affected by weak disguises, redirections, and obstructions. 

__Simplified__
Each night, the Fortune Teller may check one player’s role. This is affected by weak disguises, redirections, and obstructions. 

__Formalized__
Immediate Night: Role Investigate @Selection (SD, WD)
